title: Thyrophorella thomensis
text: Thyrophorella thomensis is a <a href="species">species</a> of small air-breathing <a href="land%20snail">land snail</a>, a <a href="terrestrial%20molluscs">terrestrial</a> <a href="pulmonate">pulmonate</a> <a href="gastropod">gastropod</a> <a href="mollusk">mollusk</a> in the family <a href="Achatinidae">Achatinidae</a>. This species is <a href="Endemism">endemic</a> to <a href="S%C3%A3o%20Tom%C3%A9%20and%20Pr%C3%ADncipe">São Tomé and Príncipe</a>.
